Andoclet
---------

This doclet creates Apache ANT Manual like documentation files out of your Ant - Sourcecodes.

There are some special annotations to deal with ANT - specifics. The doclet has localization support.

Example
---------

/**
 * @ant.description
 * This is an example Task, that shows how antdoclet works. 
 * @ant.description.de
 * Das ist eine Beispieltask, an dem die Funktionsweise von antdoclet erläutert wird. 
 * 
 * @ant.example.code
 * <helloworld display="EXAMPLE"/>
 * @ant.example.description
 * Example codes are here.
 * @ant.example.description.de
 * Beispielcodes sind hier. 
 *
 * @author centauron
 * @version 0.7
 */